News.Title: Touchwood Entertainment: Q3 Profit Soars 198% YoY to ₹3.25 Crore
News.Summary: Touchwood Entertainment reported Q3 FY25 results with revenue up 423.33% YoY to ₹36.11 crore. Net profit increased 198.17% YoY to ₹3.25 crore. EPS rose to ₹2.93, up 198.98% YoY. Operating income grew 259.35% YoY.
